Different and tasty! Made it with pierogies as a side dish. The only change I made was to heat the olive oil and then simmer the shallots in it for a minute to get rid of the raw taste. In the future, I would slice the apples and cuke ribbons into smaller pieces - it was a little unwieldy to eat.

